---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.astro";
---
<BaseLayout>
  <Navbar />
  <main style="padding: 4rem 2rem; max-width: 800px; margin: auto; text-align: left;">

    Welcome to the official doctrine of the Obsidian Empire, forged to guide our path through strife, shadow, and sovereignty.
    <section>
      <h2>👑 Emperor of Obsidian</h2>
      <p>The eternal flame that guides the Empire’s path.
        Wields final authority in all matters, ensuring balance between war, craft, diplomacy, and unity.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>🔱 The Council of Four</h2>
      <p>Our empire thrives under the leadership of four officers, each representing a pillar of our strength.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <hr/>
      <h3>⚔️ Warlord of Obsidian</h3>
      <p>The sword that cleaves chaos from order.</p>
        <section class="charter-section">
      <div class="charter-text">        
        🎯 <b>Role</b>: Military Command, PvP Strategy, Node & Castle Sieges

            Responsibilities:
        <ul>
            <li>Lead all war efforts: sieges, open-world PvP, and guild wars</li>
            <li>Train members in group tactics, counterplay, and battlefield synergy</li>
            <li>Scout enemy threats and maintain readiness</li>
            <li>Plan coordinated attack and defense strategies with allies</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="charter-image">
        <img src="assets/warlord.png"  alt="Obsidian Art" />
      </div>
      </section>
    </section>

    <section>
        <hr/>
        <h3>🛠️ Forgewarden</h3>
        <p>The fire beneath the mountain—silent, steady, and powerful.</p>
        <div class="charter-text">
        <p>
            🎯 Role: Crafting, Professions, Supply Management

            Responsibilities:
            <ul>            
                <li>Oversee gathering and processing operations</li>
                <li>Manage the Guild Crafting Planner & Resource Tracker</li>
                <li>Track profession leveling and optimize artisan roles</li>
                <li>Organize resource collection missions and caravan logistics</li>
            </ul>
        </p>
        </div>
        <div class="charter-image">
        </div>
    </section>
  
    <section>
        <hr/>
        <h3>🕵️ Shadow Envoy</h3>
        <p>A voice in silence, a dagger unseen.</p>
        <p>

            🎯 Role: Diplomacy, Intelligence, Reconnaissance

            Responsibilities:
            <ul>            
                <li>Serve as the diplomatic voice of the guild</li>
                <li>Maintain alliances, trade pacts, and war-time negotiations</li>
                <li>Gather and report intel on rival guilds or node progressions</li>
                <li>Scout enemy troop movement and guide caravan safety</li>
            </ul>
        </p>
    </section>
  
    <section>
        <hr/>
        <h3>🔥 Heartkeeper</h3>
        <p>The warmth of the hearth, the unity of the flame.</p>
        <p>
            🎯 Role: Community, Recruitment, Events

            Responsibilities:
            <ul>            
                <li>Welcome and guide new members into the guild</li>
                <li>Organize internal events and downtime games (like Gladiator Arena!)</li>
                <li>Keep morale high through celebrations, contests, and engagement</li>
                <li>Mediate member conflicts and preserve a positive environment</li>            
           </ul>
       </p>
    </section>
  

  </main>
</BaseLayout>